Alyson Stone, who was senior vice president of strategy and marketing until=
 she left in 2018 to start Attion Consulting LLC, said the videos weren=E2=
=80=99t her work. =E2=80=9CMarketing did not do this,=E2=80=9D she said. =
=E2=80=9CThis was Scott=E2=80=99s baby.=E2=80=9D The videos were used not a=
s advertisements, she said, but to boost employee morale.
=E2=80=9CThey were not universally popular within the bank, even when the b=
ank was successful,=E2=80=9D she said. =E2=80=9CIf I had had a vote, I woul=
d have voted no.=E2=80=9D

Oh me too, me too. To be fair, these videos are=C2=A0from long ago and if y=
ou had shorted the stock based on them you=E2=80=99d have had a rough decad=
e. But it=E2=80=99s the principle of the thing.

