 talks fizzled. Government Will Likely Only Sell Silicon Valley Bank to Ano=
ther Bank, Sources Say. WeWork Nears Deal for Capital Injection and Debt Co=
nversion, Sources Say. U.S. Threatens Ban if  TikTok=E2=80=99s Chinese Owne=
rs Don=E2=80=99t Sell Stakes. In New York City, a $100,000 Salary   Feels L=
