  [1] This more or less describes what seems to have   happened to Signatur=
e Bank last weekend: =E2=80=9CThe decision to take possession of the bank a=
nd hand it over to the FDIC was based on the current status of the bank and=
 its ability to do business in a safe and sound manner on Monday.=E2=80=9D


  [2] This more or less describes what seems to have  happened to Silicon V=
