he bank had a negative cash balance of approximately $958 million. Despite =
attempts from the Bank, with the assistance of regulators, to transfer coll=
ateral from various sources, the Bank did not meet its cash letter with the=
 Federal Reserve.=E2=80=9D


  [3] That=E2=80=99s from Bloomberg=E2=80=99s calculator =E2=80=94 CS 1 05/=
