<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Meanwhile, Laura Noonan at the Financial Times=
 reports that European regulators are <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomber=
gbusiness.com/click/30857809.259423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvNWU=
