<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Credit Suisse Group AG was hit with its first =
US investor lawsuit over the bank=E2=80=99s recent difficulties, alleging t=
hat it overstated its financial prospects to shareholders.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The proposed class-action complaint, filed in =
federal court in Camden, New Jersey, alleges that the bank made =E2=80=9Cma=
terially false and misleading statements=E2=80=9D in the past year that imp=
acted investors.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">To be fair, surprising financial losses at a b=
ank are a lot closer to traditional securities fraud than most of the stuff=
 I write about under the heading =E2=80=9Ceverything is securities fraud,=
=E2=80=9D but still the timing here feels a bit cruel.</p>
