=E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Another clip, made for the bank=E2=80=99s 10th=
 anniversary a decade ago, begins with the cash-register sound effects from=
 Pink Floyd=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9CMoney.=E2=80=9D Then a man in a Viking outfi=
