nk office. A child uses a sword to strike a printer that spits out, letter =
by letter, the bank=E2=80=99s name.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CNow you=E2=80=99ve come to Signature,=
=E2=80=9D a voice sings to the tune of Katy Perry=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9CFirewo=
rk.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CShow your clients what you=E2=80=99re worth.=E2=80=9D=
</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Vikings rejoice and throw their helmets. =
=E2=80=9COur profits will go up, up, up,=E2=80=9D the song goes as people d=
ance on a bar chart. =E2=80=9CWatch them grow, they=E2=80=99ll never stop.=
=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Alyson Stone, who was senior vice president of=
 strategy and marketing until she left in 2018 to start Attion Consulting L=
LC, said the videos weren=E2=80=99t her work. =E2=80=9CMarketing did not do=
 this,=E2=80=9D she said. =E2=80=9CThis was Scott=E2=80=99s baby.=E2=80=9D =
The videos were used not as advertisements, she said, but to boost employee=
 morale.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThey were not universally popular wit=
hin the bank, even when the bank was successful,=E2=80=9D she said. =E2=80=
=9CIf I had had a vote, I would have voted no.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh me too, me too. To be fair, these videos ar=
e=C2=A0from long ago and if you had shorted the stock based on them you=E2=
=80=99d have had a rough decade. But it=E2=80=99s the principle of the thin=
g.</p>
